    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一款经典即时战略游戏，在遥远的星球上为美味的奶酪而战。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >指挥你的军队</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072980/extras/30c53404d6b93a1bfe1cefd0c9377aaa.poster.avif?t=1768231841\" width=400 height=68 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072980/extras/30c53404d6b93a1bfe1cefd0c9377aaa.webm?t=1768231841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >久经考验的经典RTS操控方式，结合编队控制与快捷指令，让战斗尽在掌控之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072980/extras/07fa95855f9e9e98f83b20139b66897e.poster.avif?t=1768231841\" width=1170 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072980/extras/07fa95855f9e9e98f83b20139b66897e.webm?t=1768231841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基地建设</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集资源，建造各类建筑，训练并强化你的军队，逐步扩张你的势力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072980/extras/01c1117755916bc3f65bcb46cef608b0.poster.avif?t=1768231841\" width=1170 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072980/extras/01c1117755916bc3f65bcb46cef608b0.webm?t=1768231841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >奶酪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>奶酪</strong>是一种乳制品，由牛奶中的酪蛋白凝结而成，拥有多种风味、质地和形态。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072980/extras/2e90750d95a2c4aa4efbef3871919588.poster.avif?t=1768231841\" width=1170 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072980/extras/2e90750d95a2c4aa4efbef3871919588.webm?t=1768231841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验战役模式、遭遇战，或在多人游戏中与朋友并肩作战，争夺天梯排名。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072980/extras/83a19b4e277143f8986fa05366f69a92.poster.avif?t=1768231841\" width=1170 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072980/extras/83a19b4e277143f8986fa05366f69a92.webm?t=1768231841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
